{"tid":2495433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"吳鎮宇：政府做撚錯野，就要道歉呀！","createTime":"2021-04-19T07:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:26:17.000Z","uid":134071,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"024c3b904f212a7a4a68820225391fb7ee3177fa","tid":2495433,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dive0mfX_UM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDive0mfX_UM&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=f0f5d210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dive0mfX_UM</a><br />\n<br />\n《濁水漂流》係外國首映贏得唔少好評。鹿特丹影展更認為《濁水漂流》雖然無直接提及反送中示威, 但套戲既內容似係受到反送中示威既影響. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://iffr.com/en/2021/films/drifting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiffr.com%2Fen%2F2021%2Ffilms%2Fdrifting&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=370d18e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://iffr.com/en/2021/films/drifting</a><br />\n<br />\n不過套戲係香港首映，有d朋友負評（覺得故事散，露宿者背景交代不清），但我自己都幾like套戲，認為套戲絕對切合當今香港民情 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a9cb01d53f21c59cd7a35e81687e056f8eb749","tid":2495433,"uid":361751,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"國安法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e367e7d3b48ba20920334b5127a60d3de998f0","tid":2495433,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86a9cb01d53f21c59cd7a35e81687e056f8eb749","tid":2495433,"uid":361751,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"國安法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj